OL,3,CWelsh minister latest to resign and
OL,4,Cjoin calls for Starmer to step down
OL,6,FThe MP for Pontypridd and Minister for
OL,7,FVictims and Tackling Violence Against
OL,8,FWomen and Girls, Alex Davies-Jones,
OL,9,Fhas resigned from her ministerial role
OL,10,Fas she backs calls for the Prime
OL,11,FMinister to resign.
OL,13,FPressure has been mounting on Keir
OL,14,FStarmer to step down after election
OL,15,Fresults for Labour, not just in Wales
OL,16,Fbut also in Scotland and councils
OL,17,Facross England.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
