FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778674272
OL,3,CWelsh minister latest to resign and
OL,4,Cjoin calls for Starmer to step down
OL,6,FIn her letter to the Prime Minister,
OL,7,FMs Davies-Jones said that she is
OL,8,Fmaking the decision because she feels
OL,9,Fshe "has no choice" after
OL,10,F"catastrophic" election outcomes for
OL,11,Fher party.
OL,13,FIn her letter she said: "It has been
OL,14,Fthe honour of my life to serve his
OL,15,Fmajesty's government as the Minister
OL,16,Ffor Victims and Tackling Violence
OL,17,FAgainst Women and Girls.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778674272
OL,3,CWelsh minister latest to resign and
OL,4,Cjoin calls for Starmer to step down
OL,6,F"I have been proud to deliver some
OL,7,Fmonumental changes which will help
OL,8,Fsave lives and shift the dial on the
OL,9,Fconversation.
OL,11,F"However, we have needed to do more
OL,12,Fand therefore it is with a very, heavy
OL,13,Fheart that I feel I have no choice but
OL,14,Fto resign.
OL,16,F"The scale of the electoral defeats at
OL,17,Fthe Senedd Cymru and across the United
OL,18,FKingdom have been catastrophic."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
