FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778674272
OL,3,CWelsh minister latest to resign and
OL,4,Cjoin calls for Starmer to step down
OL,6,FShe continued that "bold" action is
OL,7,Fnow needed as a result and urged Keir
OL,8,FStarmer to announce that he will leave
OL,9,FNumber 10.
OL,11,F"I know you to be a good and honest
OL,12,Fman," she said.
OL,14,F"But in my heart are my constituents,
OL,15,Fthe victims I have had the honour of
OL,16,Fworking with every day, including the
OL,17,FHillsborough victims and their
OL,18,Ffamilies, and all those who demand
OL,19,Fbetter of us.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778674272
OL,3,CWelsh minister latest to resign and
OL,4,Cjoin calls for Starmer to step down
OL,6,F"I implore you to act in the country's
OL,7,Finterest and set out a timetable for
OL,8,Fyour departure."
OL,10,FAlex Davies-Jones has been the Labour
OL,11,FMP for Pontypridd and a serving MP
OL,12,Fsince 12 December 2019.
OL,14,FBorn in Tonyrefail, she started her
OL,15,Fpolitical career as a youth
OL,16,Frepresentative for the Labour Party,
OL,17,Fthe Co-operative Party, and Unite the
OL,18,FUnion. She later worked as a
OL,19,Fresearcher in both the House of
OL,20,FCommons and the National Assembly for
OL,21,FWales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
